{"tid":277879,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大學畢業生入息中位數，廿年來不升反跌","createTime":"2017-06-10T04:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T10:36:00.000Z","uid":716,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd39d001ea058522d155e7194b1622bd1f6309c4","tid":277879,"uid":716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:17:33.000Z","msg":"//參考政府統計處1995年至2016年的人口普查及中期人口統計資料，大學畢業生的收入中位數由<span style=\"color: red;\">1995年的16,371元</span>，逐年下降至2005年的12,978元，跌幅達21%；2010年起收入中位數雖然稍有回升，至<span style=\"color: red;\">2016年時漲至13,916元</span>，但只是勉強追回至2000年代水平，增長並不明顯。相比本港綜合消費物價指數由1995年的73.3暴漲至2016年的103.8，升幅高達41.6%，反映畢業生單憑現時的收入水平難以對抗通脹，儘管資助課程學費自1997年以來維持42,100元不變，但隨着大學生整體經濟能力下降，學債負擔愈見沉重。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/95604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F95604&d=K4QdYdPxXcZORePJNRKbpB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=74b8e1eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/95604</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">利申：Fresh grad</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3cb2fb3ad0f5a514c0f775f1931866b7debc85","tid":277879,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:37:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"268c8c7e260831d866da3d2a6761ed92b3caeeed","tid":277879,"uid":113956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"珠海果堆都當係degree 自然拉低哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b055eb856eeadfbf3603394c90f921fff1a1032","tid":277879,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:58:17.000Z","msg":"打壓80 90 後有冇數據證明。 咁又點？ 咪又係無人出聲 繼續當無事發生過 繼續去爭住做賤價既工"},{"pid":"2b706cd293064a86247f7794eb6e8a43ab5980e0","tid":277879,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打壓80 90 後有哂數據證明。 咁又點？ 咪又係無人出聲 繼續當無事發生過 繼續去爭住做賤價既工</blockquote>"},{"pid":"bf6264e63